A massive lithium deposit, estimated at 40 million metric tons =E2=80=94 th=
at=E2=80=99s 80 billion pounds =E2=80=94 was discovered in the McDermitt Ca=
ldera on the Oregon-Nevada border a few years back. It=E2=80=99s the larges=
t known lithium deposit in the world and it sits right here on U.S. of A so=
il. The deposit is believed to have formed due to volcanic activity and the=
 subsequent evaporation of lithium-rich waters, concentrating the mineral i=
