tps://substack.com/redirect/4deed84a-06d5-495e-a8bd-fcb2212baf7b?j=3DeyJ1Ij=
oiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ]=20
Packy again. In the last piece of 2024, I wrote The Return of Magic [ https=
://substack.com/redirect/4a93e7dc-0836-4e06-ba60-c54f4608c8f0?j=3DeyJ1IjoiO=
XAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ]. In it, I talked ab=
